Description: Performs nested k*l-fold cross-validation for the 'glmnet' and 
    'caret' packages, including cross-validation of 'glmnet' alpha parameter and 
    fast filter functions for feature selection. 
    Stone M (1977). "An Asymptotic Equivalence of Choice of Model by 
    Cross-Validation and Akaike's Criterion". Journal of the Royal Statistical 
